---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import site from '@/lib/site';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Recovery &amp; Detox IV Therapy | Menon Medispa | Millburn, NJ"
  description="Recovery and detox IV drip therapy in Millburn NJ. Flush toxins, rehydrate, and restore nutrients after workouts, illness, or a late night."
>
  <main class="sp" data-slug="recovery-detox">

    <section class="sp-hero" aria-label="Recovery &amp; Detox IV Therapy in Millburn NJ">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div class="sp-hero__grid">
          <div class="sp-hero__content">
            <h1 class="sp-hero__title">Recovery &amp; Detox IV Therapy in Millburn NJ</h1>
            <p class="sp-hero__eyebrow">Your fastest way to reset, replenish, and recover.</p>
            <p class="sp-hero__lead">Whether you're recovering from a hard workout, an illness, jet lag, or just a long night, our Recovery &amp; Detox IV drip in Millburn, NJ delivers rapid relief by flushing toxins, restoring hydration, and replenishing vital nutrients.</p>
            <div class="sp-hero__actions">
              <a class="sp-btn sp-btn--gold" href="/consultation">Book Your IV Therapy</a>
            </div>
            <div class="sp-reviews">
              <div class="sp-reviews__avatars">
                <img src="/images/90411e0041df.png" alt="Client review" width="44" height="44" />
                <img src="/images/305afeda5f9a.png" alt="Client review" width="44" height="44" />
                <img src="/images/b95880091b44.png" alt="Client review" width="44" height="44" />
              </div>
              <div class="sp-reviews__text">
                <span class="sp-reviews__stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</span>
                <span class="sp-reviews__count">100+ 5 Star Reviews</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <img class="sp-hero__img" src="/images/651c7c197b52.png" alt="Recovery &amp; Detox IV Therapy in Millburn NJ" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-badges" aria-label="Highlights">
      <div class="sp-container sp-badges__row">
        <p class="sp-badge"><span class="sp-badge__check">&#10003;</span> Rapid Rehydration</p>
        <p class="sp-badge"><span class="sp-badge__check">&#10003;</span> Flush Toxins</p>
        <p class="sp-badge"><span class="sp-badge__check">&#10003;</span> Restore Electrolytes</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-plain" aria-label="Formulas">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;">
          <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(1.75rem,3vw,2.25rem);color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 1.5rem;">Choose Your Formula</h2>
          <div style="background:#f8f4f0;padding:1.5rem;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
            <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-xl);color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.4rem;">RECOVERY Signature</h3>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);font-style:italic;color:#6a6470;margin:0 0 0.75rem;font-size:var(--text-sm);">Best for rapid rehydration and relief from fatigue, dehydration, or hangovers.</p>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0 0 0.75rem;line-height:1.7;">This targeted formula is designed to get you feeling better, fast, by delivering the essential nutrients your body needs to recover most efficiently.</p>
            <ul style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;line-height:1.8;padding-left:1.5rem;margin:0;"><li>Vitamin C &amp; Glutathione: Powerful antioxidants that neutralize toxins, combat the oxidative stress that causes fatigue, and support the liver's detoxification process.</li><li>B12 &amp; Taurine: Help restore your natural energy and metabolic function quickly after depletion.</li><li>Minerals: A foundational electrolyte blend to restore hydration at a cellular level and correct the imbalances that cause headaches and fatigue.</li></ul>
          </div><div style="background:#f8f4f0;padding:1.5rem;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
            <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-xl);color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.4rem;">RECOVERY Deluxe</h3>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);font-style:italic;color:#6a6470;margin:0 0 0.75rem;font-size:var(--text-sm);">Best for comprehensive recovery from intense physical exertion, illness, or deep detoxification.</p>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0 0 0.75rem;line-height:1.7;">This advanced formula is designed for a deeper, more comprehensive recovery and full-body reset. Includes the Signature foundation, plus:</p>
            <ul style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;line-height:1.8;padding-left:1.5rem;margin:0;"><li>Complete B-Complex: Restores the B-vitamins depleted during physical stress, supporting cellular energy production and faster tissue repair.</li><li>Magnesium &amp; Zinc: Critical minerals that reduce inflammation, relax tense muscles, and support the immune system as it recovers.</li><li>Amino Acids: Accelerate muscle repair and reduce post-exertion soreness, getting you back to your best faster.</li></ul>
          </div>
          <p style="margin-top:2rem;"><a class="sp-btn sp-btn--gold" href="/consultation">Schedule Now</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-photos" aria-label="Customer Photos">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div class="sp-photos__head"><h2>Hear From Our Customers!</h2></div>
        <div class="sp-photos__grid">
          <img src="/images/9ebaca3843d3.jpg" alt="IV Therapy customer" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/images/6c461885a28e.jpg" alt="IV Therapy customer" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/images/823792ea5ead.jpg" alt="IV Therapy customer" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/images/cd675890fe0d.jpg" alt="IV Therapy customer" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/images/2e5d1e68225a.jpg" alt="IV Therapy customer" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-plain sp-plain--alt" aria-label="Process">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;">
          <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(1.75rem,3vw,2.25rem);color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 1.5rem;">Simple, Relaxing, and Effective</h2>
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;">
            <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;">
              <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-2xl);color:var(--color-accent-warm);flex-shrink:0;line-height:1;">01</span>
              <div><h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.25rem;">Personalized Consultation</h3><p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0;line-height:1.7;">Your session begins with a brief consultation with one of our registered nurses. They will review your wellness goals and answer any questions to ensure your treatment is perfectly suited to your needs.</p></div>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;">
              <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-2xl);color:var(--color-accent-warm);flex-shrink:0;line-height:1;">02</span>
              <div><h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.25rem;">Relax and Recharge</h3><p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0;line-height:1.7;">Once settled in our comfortable therapy lounge, the IV drip is administered. The process is virtually painless and takes about 45-60 minutes. You can relax, read, or catch up on emails while your body absorbs the nutrients.</p></div>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;">
              <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-2xl);color:var(--color-accent-warm);flex-shrink:0;line-height:1;">03</span>
              <div><h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.25rem;">Feel the Benefits</h3><p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0;line-height:1.7;">Many clients report immediate benefits after their session. The nutrients continue to work for days, supporting your body's natural processes and helping you feel and look your best.</p></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-pricing" aria-label="Pricing">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div class="sp-pricing__head">
          <h2>Book Your IV Therapy</h2>
          <p style="font-style:italic;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">All IV Drips are 500ml. Upgrade to 1000ml for only $25</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sp-pricelist">
          <div class="sp-priceitem">
            <img class="sp-priceitem__thumb" src="/images/651c7c197b52.png" alt="RECOVERY (Signature)" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="sp-priceitem__main">
              <a class="sp-priceitem__title" href="/booking-calendar/recovery-signature">RECOVERY (Signature)</a>
              <p class="sp-priceitem__sub">500ml.</p>
              <a class="sp-priceitem__readmore" href="/service-page/recovery-signature">Read More</a>
            </div>
            <div class="sp-priceitem__price">$200</div>
            <a class="sp-btn sp-btn--gold sp-priceitem__cta" href="/booking-calendar/recovery-signature">Request to Book</a>
          </div>
          <div class="sp-priceitem">
            <img class="sp-priceitem__thumb" src="/images/651c7c197b52.png" alt="RECOVERY (Deluxe)" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="sp-priceitem__main">
              <a class="sp-priceitem__title" href="/booking-calendar/recovery-deluxe">RECOVERY (Deluxe)</a>
              <p class="sp-priceitem__sub">500ml.</p>
              <a class="sp-priceitem__readmore" href="/service-page/recovery-deluxe">Read More</a>
            </div>
            <div class="sp-priceitem__price">$250</div>
            <a class="sp-btn sp-btn--gold sp-priceitem__cta" href="/booking-calendar/recovery-deluxe">Request to Book</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-testimonial" aria-label="What Our Clients Say">
      <img class="sp-testimonial__bg" src="/images/30cfb9e87c60.png" alt="" width="1440" height="626" loading="lazy" />
      <div class="sp-testimonial__overlay"></div>
      <div class="sp-container sp-testimonial__inner">
        <h2 class="sp-script-title sp-script-title--light" style="margin-bottom:2rem;">What Our <em>Clients</em> Say</h2>
        <blockquote class="sp-quote">
          <span class="sp-quote__mark">&ldquo;</span>
          Jennifer is amazing. Her aura and energy makes you feel welcomed and comfortable. Love our sessions! And my girl Rose Marie, the receptionist, is just lovely! I always leave with great joy after seeing them.
          <cite>Alexa C.</cite>
        </blockquote>
        <img src="/images/5be44787b3a9.png" alt="5 Star Google Reviews" width="143" height="74" loading="lazy" style="margin-top:1.75rem;" />
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-faq" aria-label="Frequently asked questions">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div class="sp-faq__card">
          <div class="sp-faq__head"><h2 class="sp-faq__title">Frequently asked questions</h2></div>
          <div class="sp-faq__list">
            <details class="sp-faq__item" open>
              <summary>How quickly will I feel better after the Recovery IV drip?</summary>
              <div class="sp-faq__answer"><p>Most clients begin to feel significantly better within 30-60 minutes of starting the IV drip, with full recovery often felt within a few hours. The direct-to-bloodstream delivery of hydration and nutrients works much faster than drinking water or taking oral supplements.</p></div>
            </details>
            <details class="sp-faq__item">
              <summary>Is the Recovery IV drip safe for post-workout recovery?</summary>
              <div class="sp-faq__answer"><p>Absolutely. It's an excellent tool for serious athletes. By rapidly replenishing fluids, electrolytes, and amino acids lost during intense exercise, it significantly accelerates muscle repair and reduces the soreness and fatigue associated with hard training sessions.</p></div>
            </details>
            <details class="sp-faq__item">
              <summary>Can the detox IV drip help with jet lag?</summary>
              <div class="sp-faq__answer"><p>Yes, it's very effective. Jet lag is essentially a combination of dehydration, disrupted nutrient balance, and fatigue—all things our Recovery drip is designed to address. Many clients find it helps them feel back to normal much more quickly after long flights.</p></div>
            </details>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-cta" aria-label="Get Back to 100%, Fast">
      <div class="sp-container sp-cta__grid">
        <div class="sp-cta__copy">
          <h2 class="sp-cta__title">Get Back to 100%, Fast</h2>
          <p class="sp-cta__sub">Menon Medispa Millburn NJ</p>
          <p>Don't suffer through slow recovery. Schedule your Recovery &amp; Detox IV therapy at Menon Medispa in Millburn, NJ and feel yourself again.</p>
          <a class="sp-btn sp-btn--gold" href="/consultation">Schedule Free Consultation</a>
        </div>
        <div class="sp-cta__media">
          <img src="/images/b1a819f35921.webp" alt="Menon Office Staff" width="431" height="560" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</BaseLayout>
